\fs52 \cf0 Ambrosia Macaroons\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\ql\qnatural

\b0\fs26 \cf0 Southerners love ambrosia, a sumptuous m\'e9lange of sliced juicy-sweet oranges and freshly grated coconut. This sweet salad has been a part of southern Christmas traditions for the better part of two centuries. This recipe uses the coconut-orange combo in a new way, adding finely grated orange peel to classic coconut macaroons, then drizzling the cookies with bittersweet chocolate for a festive finish.\
makes about 45\
